    {
      "id": "armadoggo",
      "name": "铠护犬功能速查",
      "description": "铠护犬命令与装备",
      "order": 4,
      "type": "mixed_content",
      "content_blocks": [
        {
          "block_type": "info_card",
          "title": "TEST",
          "icon_url": "",
          "mdi_icon": "",
          "highlight": "",
          "descriptions": [
            {
              "text": "如果伴随模式下的铠护犬快被杀死，它将挖洞逃走，一小时后满血出现。它逃走后背包里的物品将留在原地，除非它装备了随伴的背包",
              "bold": false,
              "color": "auto",
              "opacity": 1,
              "server": "",
              "server_states": {}
            }
          ],
          "icon_auto_color": false,
          "quote_color": "#2196F3",
          "collapse_descriptions": true,
          "title_color": "#2196F3",
          "server_states": {
            "_hint": 2
          }
        },
        {
          "block_type": "info_card",
          "title": "",
          "icon_url": "",
          "mdi_icon": "",
          "highlight": "",
          "descriptions": [
            {
              "text": "当一只处于伴随模式的铠甲犬击败野生食肉动物或腐化生物时，有几率获得一张六角污染物地图。这张地图类似普通宝藏地图，但只有伴随模式下的铠甲犬进入指定地点后才能挖掘出宝藏，战利品会附带一个随机装备特性",
              "bold": false,
              "color": "auto",
              "opacity": 1,
              "server": "",
              "server_states": {}
            }
          ],
          "icon_auto_color": false,
          "quote_color": "#2196F3",
          "collapse_descriptions": false,
          "title_color": "#2196F3",
          "server_states": {
            "_hint": 1
          }
        },
        {
          "block_type": "info_card",
          "title": "警告",
          "icon_url": "",
          "mdi_icon": "",
          "highlight": "",
          "descriptions": [
            {
              "text": "传图前务必解除伴随模式，否则铠护犬将永久丢失",
              "bold": false,
              "color": "auto",
              "opacity": 1,
              "server": "",
              "server_states": {}
            }
          ],
          "icon_auto_color": false,
          "quote_color": "#FF9800",
          "collapse_descriptions": false,
          "title_color": "#FF9800",
          "server_states": {
            "_warn": 2
          }
        },
        {
          "block_type": "divider",
          "style": "wavy",
          "title": "TEST",
          "color": "auto",
          "title_bold": true
        },
        {
          "block_type": "info_card",
          "title": "Sit 坐下",
          "icon_url": "https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858216257-55486547-c297-403e-bcd2-b786b9617814.png",
          "mdi_icon": "",
          "highlight": "",
          "descriptions": [
            {
              "text": "将坐下并待在原位，直到被玩家要求移动",
              "bold": false,
              "color": "auto",
              "opacity": 1,
              "server": "",
              "server_states": {}
            }
          ],
          "icon_auto_color": true,
          "title_color": "auto",
          "server_states": {},
          "quote_color": "auto",
          "collapse_descriptions": false
        },
        {
          "block_type": "info_card",
          "title": "Fetch! 取来！",
          "icon_url": "https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858339850-9abb2dfd-0335-4838-95ba-a17e1832e7fd.png",
          "mdi_icon": "",
          "highlight": "",
          "descriptions": [
            {
              "text": "将收集地上掉落的任何附近包裹",
              "bold": false,
              "color": "auto",
              "opacity": 1,
              "server": "",
              "server_states": {}
            }
          ],
          "icon_auto_color": true,
          "title_color": "auto",
          "server_states": {},
          "quote_color": "auto",
          "collapse_descriptions": false
        },
        {
          "block_type": "info_card",
          "title": "Play Dead! 装死！",
          "icon_url": "https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858343396-e5660531-69fd-4ab8-b79a-612ab940b7e2.png",
          "mdi_icon": "",
          "highlight": "",
          "descriptions": [
            {
              "text": "将躺在地上几秒钟，此时它将受到85%的减伤效果，野生生物将忽视它。它有30秒的冷却时间",
              "bold": false,
              "color": "auto",
              "opacity": 1,
              "server": "",
              "server_states": {}
            }
          ],
          "icon_auto_color": true,
          "title_color": "auto",
          "server_states": {},
          "quote_color": "auto",
          "collapse_descriptions": true
        },
        {
          "block_type": "info_card",
          "title": "Who's There? 谁在那里？",
          "icon_url": "https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858347879-ff609eca-3cf5-4c8a-81e4-2dd3c95e69ec.png",
          "mdi_icon": "",
          "highlight": "",
          "descriptions": [
            {
              "text": "将警告您附近的野生恐龙或敌人",
