          "collapse_descriptions": false
        },
        {
          "block_type": "info_card",
          "title": "Here Pup! 过来，小狗！",
          "icon_url": "https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858367531-884f3a4e-d0f5-4782-95bb-9be27be25342.png",
          "mdi_icon": "",
          "highlight": "",
          "descriptions": [
            {
              "text": "无论距离有多远，都会到你身边。如果玩家距离较远，会在挖洞到达玩家身边，避免受伤。冷却时间为120秒",
